22
0:1:12,8 --> 0:1:16,8
'He's an artist.


23
0:1:16,8 --> 0:1:17,24
'Sort of.'


24
0:1:17,24 --> 0:1:21,32
'London was her place -
definite and focused, like her mind.


25
0:1:21,32 --> 0:1:23,92
'The home of her triumphs
and tragedies.'


26
0:1:23,92 --> 0:1:26,88
'This is Mike.'


27
0:1:26,88 --> 0:1:28,28
'He's my best friend.


28
